{"tid":2102262,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"美國制裁涉疆中國官員　趙立堅稱中方將採對等措施：「很快你就會知道」","createTime":"2020-07-10T10:40:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T14:23:06.000Z","uid":79563,"like":146,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":113,"replies":[{"pid":"542d98b4e9dc16ade8b6ab347036160e79e7861d","tid":2102262,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T10:40:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537005-20200710.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537005-20200710.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumg5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=f1477554\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537005-20200710.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=d12d4f1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537005-20200710.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n美國宣布向4名中國新疆官員實施制裁，包括新疆維吾爾自治區黨委書記、中共政治局委員陳全國，指他們嚴重侵犯新疆維吾爾族的人權。<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部發言人趙立堅表示堅決反對及強烈譴責，決定對在涉疆問題上表現惡劣的美國個人及機構採取對等措施，敦促美方立即撤銷錯誤決定，停止任何干涉中國內政、損害中方利益的言行。被問到進一步制裁美方的措施細節，趙立堅回答記者「很快你就會知道」。"},{"pid":"b868093bf8e068b53fd1b14ad810a36bd0c612e6","tid":2102262,"uid":230104,"like":54,"dislike":1,"score":53,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T10:41:59.000Z","msg":"講就兇狠，做就"},{"pid":"9fd2f65a8e1a0c3c389265b10c6ac609fa9c6fd0","tid":2102262,"uid":4780,"like":83,"dislike":0,"score":83,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T10:42:19.000Z","msg":"送中國護照比侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><p class=\"left\"></p>"},{"pid":"bbff7b8eda93179ca7c3af6685edb3dd462f7bfd","tid":2102262,"uid":10340,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T10:42:39.000Z","msg":"面目可憎就係形容呢條友個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dde3e8d468f578a76b3493c4a431c61fc607b2f","tid":2102262,"uid":32782,"li